@model IEnumerable<SuMejorPeso.Models.Classroom>
@using SuMejorPeso.Models 
@* --- INICIO: AÑADIR ESTE BLOQUE --- *@
@if (TempData["SuccessMessage"] != null)
{
    <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
        @TempData["SuccessMessage"]
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
    </div>
}
@if (TempData["ErrorMessage"] != null)
{
    <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
        @TempData["ErrorMessage"]
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert" aria-label="Close"></button>
    </div>
}
@* --- FIN: AÑADIR ESTE BLOQUE --- *@

@{ ViewData["Title"] = $"Clases en {ViewBag.BranchName}"; }

<h1 class="margen-barra">Clases Disponibles en @ViewBag.BranchName</h1>
<p><a asp-action="Branches">Cambiar de Sede</a></p>
@if (!Model.Any())
{
    <p>No hay clases activas en esta sede por el momento.</p>
}
else
{
    <div class="row">
        @foreach (var classroom in Model)
        {
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-3 ">
                <div class="card h-100 ">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title">@classroom.name</h5>
                        <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">@classroom.assignment.name</h6>
                        <p class="card-text">@classroom.description</p>
                        <p><small>Cupo: @classroom.members.Count() / @classroom.limitedPlace</small></p>
                        <p><small>Profesor(es): @string.Join(", ", classroom.coaches.Select(c => c.name))</small></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-footer">
                        @if (User.IsInRole(UserRole.member.ToString())) //
                        {
                            // TODO: Implementar acción de inscripción
                            <form asp-controller="Classrooms" asp-action="Enroll" method="post">
                                <input type="hidden" name="classroomId" value="@classroom.id" />
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-success" disabled="@(classroom.members.Count() >= classroom.limitedPlace)">
                                    @(classroom.members.Count() >= classroom.limitedPlace ? "Clase Llena" : "Inscribirse")
                                </button>
                            </form>
                        }
                        else if (User.IsInRole(UserRole.defaults.ToString())) //
                        {
                            <a asp-controller="MembershipStore" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-sm btn-warning">
                                Necesitas ser Miembro para inscribirte
                            </a>
                        }
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        }
    </div>
}